        "text_kxEzid": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "This is not a wine class",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>This is not a wine class.</strong></p><p>A TerraVino private tasting is an evening built around a single idea: that the best way to understand Italian wine is to drink it well, in good company, without leaving home.</p><p>We bring a curated flight of bottles from unique family-run estates across Italy, producers who often don't advertise, don't scale, and don't compromise. Each wine is chosen for the occasion and tailored to the people at the table. A food spread designed to complement the selection arrives with us.</p><p>What unfolds over the next two and a half hours is part tasting, part conversation, part celebration of life. Guests leave knowing more than they arrived with, and with at least one producer they'll remember by name.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
